### Word Problem Tool

#### 2-step word problem

**Ramu has 10 apples. He gives 3 apples to his friend. Then he buys 5 more apples. How many apples does Ramu have now?**

#### 1-step word problem

**Ramu has 10 apples. He gives 3 apples to his friend. How many apples does Ramu have left?**

